Functional Requirements

The functional requirements describe what CookSnap â€“ Smart Recipe Recommendation System Using Grocery Images must do to support ingredient 
detection and recipe recommendation.

FR-01: Grocery Image Upload

Description:
The system shall allow users to upload images of available groceries.

Acceptance Criteria:

User can successfully upload an image

Uploaded image is stored for processing

System validates supported image formats

FR-02: Ingredient Detection

Description:
The system shall automatically detect grocery items from the uploaded image using image recognition techniques.

Acceptance Criteria:

Detected ingredients are displayed to the user

Ingredient list is generated accurately

Detection process completes successfully

FR-03: Recipe Recommendation

Description:
The system shall recommend suitable recipes based on the detected ingredients.

Acceptance Criteria:

Recommended recipes match detected ingredients

At least one relevant recipe is displayed

Recommendations are updated based on ingredient changes

FR-04: Recipe Details Display

Description:
The system shall display detailed information for selected recipes.

Acceptance Criteria:

Recipe ingredients and preparation steps are shown

Instructions are clear and easy to understand

FR-05: Recipe Filtering

Description:
The system shall allow users to filter recipes based on preferences.

Acceptance Criteria:

User can apply filters (e.g., vegetarian / non-vegetarian)

Filtered results update correctly

FR-06: User Authentication

Description:
The system shall provide secure login access for registered users and administrators.

Acceptance Criteria:

Only authorized users can log in

Invalid login attempts are rejected

FR-07: Admin Dashboard Access

Description:
The system shall provide an admin dashboard for system monitoring and management.

Acceptance Criteria:

Admin can view system usage statistics

Admin can manage recipe data and user access

FR-08: Basic Report Generation

Description:
The system shall generate basic system reports.

Acceptance Criteria:

Reports include number of users and recipes viewed

Reports can be viewed or downloaded
